1 unit(s) Canned tuna
1 unit(s) Hard Boiled Egg
113 g Baby Tomatoes
56 g Spring Mix
30 g Mixed Olives
1 tbsp Red Wine Vinegar
tsp Salt*
0.06 tsp Pepper*
tbsp Oil*

Halve tomatoes.
Drain, then cut or tear olives in half.
Drain tuna.
Quarter egg.

Arrange spring mix in a bowl.
Top with tuna, tomatoes, eggs and olives.
Drizzle 1/2 tbsp oil and as much vinegar as desired over top, then season with salt and pepper.